is so much closer to "curse."

16:50.927 --> 16:52.337
What?

16:54.764 --> 16:56.300
Stop it!

16:56.391 --> 16:58.882
Before I speak with them,
notdunng.

16:58.977 --> 17:01.309
She's an ignorant creature.

17:01.396 --> 17:05.560
John Crichton, Prince Clavor,
our second-in-line
to the throne.

17:05.650 --> 17:08.562
First among my people.

17:08.653 --> 17:12.020
You may take the guards and
leave us now, Tyno.

17:12.115 --> 17:14.106
My instructions are otherwise.

17:14.201 --> 17:20.162
This potential suitor to the
throne is to remain under
protective custody at all times.

17:20.248 --> 17:22.955
And whose order dares to
countermand mine?

17:23.043 --> 17:24.499
The Empress.

17:24.586 --> 17:26.292
Your mother.

17:34.346 --> 17:37.008
I will speak with you...

17:37.098 --> 17:38.599
later.

17:44.189 --> 17:48.683
There's always one in
every family.

17:48.777 --> 17:52.941
lf Princess Katralla fails to
wed by the anniversary
of her birth

17:53.031 --> 17:55.317
the throne goes to
Prince Clavor.

17:55.408 --> 17:57.615
Uh-huh. When's the expiry day?

17:57.702 --> 17:59.693
A matter of solar days.

18:02.332 --> 18:04.038
Is this my cell?

18:04.125 --> 18:05.456
Your room, yes.

18:10.048 --> 18:11.413
(sighs)

18:14.177 --> 18:16.168
Where have you two been?

18:16.263 --> 18:18.879
We've been in the Space Command
Center all night.

18:18.974 --> 18:21.056
Moya is no longer in orbit
around this planet.

18:21.142 --> 18:25.181
And Flight Control confirmed
that she didn't crash, so Zhaan
and Pilot probably just...

18:25.272 --> 18:26.762
Starburst away and abandoned us.

18:26.856 --> 18:28.721
If we wanted to jump
to conclusions.

18:28.817 --> 18:30.227
You know Crichton's in custody.

18:30.318 --> 18:31.558
What?!
-Mm-hmm.

18:31.653 --> 18:33.894
He kissed some Princess and
now they won't let him go.

18:33.989 --> 18:35.650
Of all the stupid...

18:35.740 --> 18:37.150
